{"tid":2390716,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【突發】券商Robinhood再緊急融資24億美金","createTime":"2021-02-01T17:49:51.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-02T00:22:36.000Z","uid":259777,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"ff93bd68df24889605ffa25017c5d9bc73adc2d8","tid":2390716,"uid":259777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T17:49:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53ece574575d68526bb0b5152a3d164d6c2eba1a","tid":2390716,"uid":88133,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T17:50:43.000Z","msg":"240億都唔知夠唔夠<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db8e82fffb203199f969dee4da397940df944f2d","tid":2390716,"uid":274352,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T17:51:15.000Z","msg":"醬汁？"},{"pid":"4c31b9b6f5bfc7a777f64936d7c3e184c7965768","tid":2390716,"uid":66377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T17:51:27.000Z","msg":"邊夠呀24億"},{"pid":"a18c5a139df0bd9fc0b8f3f2ccaa3ccbb1359362","tid":2390716,"uid":259777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T17:51:45.000Z","msg":"Robinhood raises another $2.4 billion as broker app deals with retail trading frenzy<br />\n<br />\nDiscount online brokerage Robinhood said Monday it has raised another $2.4 billion from investors amid the extreme bouts of market volatility.<br />\n<br />\nThe $3.4 billion it has mobilized since Thursday exceeds the total amount it has raised since its founding in 2013.<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">&ldquo;This funding is a strong sign of confidence from investors and will help us build for the future and continue to serve people through the exponential growth we&rsquo;ve seen this year,&rdquo; the company said.</span><br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;We&rsquo;re witnessing a movement of everyday people taking control of their own financial futures, many investing for the first time through Robinhood.&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">It said it will use the new funding to expand its programs on financial literacy.</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;With this funding, we&rsquo;ll build and enhance our products that give more people access to the financial system,&rdquo; the company&rsquo;s statement said.<br />\n<br />\nRobinhood has been in the center of the storm around a move by retail investors over the past week that has squeezed hedge funds that bet big against stocks including GameStop and AMC Entertainment.<br />\n<br />\nAs shares in the companies surged, Robinhood placed extreme limits on how much their customers, mainly younger and small-dollar investors, could buy. The company narrowed that list Monday from about 50 to eight.<br />\n<br />\nInvestors who had met up online, in particular on Reddit&rsquo;s WallStreetBets forum, snapped up shares of the companies, forcing some institutional firms into losses. The moves set off a vicious round of volatility on Wall Street that saw the Dow industrials lose close to 3%."},{"pid":"2ad212f5056f73d9646b2fe51850b8a548328216","tid":2390716,"uid":47920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T17:52:20.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.cnbc.com/2021/02/01/robinhood-raises-another-2point4-billion-as-broker-app-deals-with-retail-trading-frenzy.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbc.com%2F2021%2F02%2F01%2Frobinhood-raises-another-2point4-billion-as-broker-app-deals-with-retail-trading-frenzy.html&d=FyOxfEvlGqeE3CGJWKQQl2bkIIQgOyZVEIOEDwMYbAQ%3D&h=5bdb7beb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.cnbc.com/2021/02/01/robinhood-raises-another-2point4-billion-as-broker-app-deals-with-retail-trading-frenzy.html</a>"},{"pid":"c7e9ecd9c273732384fdc10a20e1